# Source Code Directory

This is where your business code lives.

## Structure

Organize your code according to the architecture guidelines in `docs/architecture/`.

### Example Go Structure

```
src/
├── cmd/
│   └── server/
│       └── main.go
├── internal/
│   ├── handler/
│   ├── service/
│   └── repository/
└── pkg/
```

### Example Frontend Structure

```
src/
├── components/
├── pages/
├── hooks/
├── services/
└── types/
```

## Guidelines

- Follow coding standards in `ai/rules/coding.md`
- Run harness before committing
- Keep functions under 50 lines
- Maintain test coverage above 80%
